      String ViewDrawingCommand.execute(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request, javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse response, FunctionManager manager)
      Retrieves attribute order from session and the carport drawing is generated based on the details from the order - the carport is saved on session, while carportDrawing is saved on request - forward to viewdrawing.jsp
      String ViewPartlistCommand.execute(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request, javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse response, FunctionManager manager)
      Retrieves attribute user from session - forward to partlist.jsp if user is admin or employee - forward to customerpartlist.jsp if user is customer
